sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant C as AuthController
    participant S as AuthService
    participant O as OtpService
    participant DB as Database
    participant E as EmailService

    U->>C: Signup / Login request
    C->>S: process request

    alt Signup
        S->>DB: create user (email_verified=false)
        S->>O: generate OTP
        O->>DB: save OTP
        O->>E: send OTP email
        E-->>U: OTP code
    end

    alt Verify OTP
        U->>C: submit OTP
        C->>S: verify OTP
        S->>DB: mark email_verified=true
    end